data.name: [SFDC-341] Import Stripe Primary Email to Account Records
data.notes:
Per ticket:
[https://verifiedfirst.atlassian.net/browse/SSCSF-592|https://verifiedfirst.atlassian.net/browse/SSCSF-592]
It was discovered that the account field ‘Stripe Primary Email’ is required to create any payment objects on an account. However, field is not present on all account records.
Need to run a report to identify all accounts with account record type = GCS Account or record type = Traditional Account with Stripe Primary Email = NULL

From those accounts identify the appropriate email from another location (statistical contact email, authorized purchaser email, Billing contact email, etc.) on the account and populate in mass the Stripe Primary Email to identified account records

This will prevent issues when importing Invoice objects and processing future payments on accounts
